<h3>Server Path to electronic goods</h3><p>This is the full path to where you want your electronic goods to be uploaded if you are selling any.&nbsp; Electronic goods are downloadable items.&nbsp; This would be the folder name on your server where the items should be uploaded.&nbsp;</p><p>TIP:&nbsp; This should be outside your publicly accessable web folder.&nbsp; </p><p>For instance, if your website is located on drive C of the server hosting your site and you want your egoods to go into the folder egoods, then this would be:</p><p>C:#request.bslash#egoods#request.bslash#</p><p>If you are hosting your website with a host provider then contact them to find out what the path names are to your website folders.&nbsp; Most host providers have this information accessable in online documentation.</p><p>For UplinkEarth users use the FTP path.&nbsp; For example, if my domain is cfshopkart.com on UplinkEarth, then the path to mine would look like this:</p><p>/cfshopkart_com/egoods/</p>




